<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Phytomyzinae" genus="Phytobia" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Phytobia amelanchieris" order="Diptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="amelanchieris">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Phytobia amelanchieris</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, but colour of the palpus, gena and parafacial will still differentiate the two.
</paragraph>
